BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tablesf/fifa-wcc2013.html
Season: 2013
Competition: FIFA Club World Cup

*Participants
*FC Bayern München (Germany)        - 2012/13 UEFA Champions' League winners
*Club Atlético Mineiro (Brazil)     - 2013 Copa Libertadores winners
*Guangzhou Evergrande (China)       - 2013 Asian Champions' League winners
*CF Monterrey (Mexico)              - 2012/13 FC Champions Cup winners
*Auckland City FC (New Zealand)     - 2012/13 Oceanian Champions' Cup winners
*Al-Ahly (Cairo) (Egypt)            - 2013 African Champions' Cup winners
*Raja Casablanca (Morocco)          - 2012/13 Moroccan Championship winners

Round: 1
12/11/2013;  Raja Casablanca     ;  2-1; Auckland City      ;          Agadir

Round: 2

12/14/2013; Guangzhou Evergrande ; 2-0; Al-Ahly                     ; Agadir
12/14/2013; Raja Casablanca      ; 2-1 (aet); Monterrey             ; Agadir

Round: Semi Finals
12/17/2013; Guangzhou Evergrande ; 0-3; Bayern München    ;           Agadir
12/18/2013; Raja Casablanca      ; 3-1; Atlético Mineiro  ;           Marrakech

Round: 5th Place

12/18/2013; Al-Ahly              ; 1-5; Monterrey    ;                Marrakech

Round: 3rd Place

12/21/2013; Guangzhou Evergrande ; 2-3; Atlético Mineiro   ;          Marrakech      

Round: Final 

12/21/2013  ; Bayern München      ;  2-0; Raja Casablanca       ;       Marrakech   


